
Ranger Help for: rest
=====================

SYNTAX:      rest
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,inside,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   7
BASE SP:     35 sp
SKILL TYPE:  aid

SUMMARY:    
When a Ranger rests, he or she finds a cozy spot in the wilderness and
lies down for a good nap. While resting, the Ranger heals at an
increased rate, but he or she can't do or see anything. Length of resting
periods is variable and theres is no way to break it.

